function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != 'c05bc188215142f9253ada89ffb37dbfdc604217') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== 'c05bc188215142f9253ada89ffb37dbfdc604217') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '6e2045f3fd200b422ef6852a8556631a811d6d65') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== 'c05bc188215142f9253ada89ffb37dbfdc604217') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/config_values.txt')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/config_values.txt');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('doc/config_values.txt')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/config_values.txt');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') != 'ac09672e4100dba21d05ef88487f991812358e77') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.txt');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/config_values.txt', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/config_values.txt');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== 'ac09672e4100dba21d05ef88487f991812358e77') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== '8662b4923a2b23e1939b3102f946da6790ce9382') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/config_values.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/config_values.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/config_values.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/config_values.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== 'ac09672e4100dba21d05ef88487f991812358e77') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.txt');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') != '322b901bf1ff5af993b38359fb18dc4c41a9d13d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== '322b901bf1ff5af993b38359fb18dc4c41a9d13d') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== '804e2c89c9c1b9e7636d3360e93217e65b0f584c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== '322b901bf1ff5af993b38359fb18dc4c41a9d13d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGetterSetterInterface.class.php') != '5de95b14c419a17b39e8c14ea69d53a2aa0e9fd4') {

	}

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGetterSetterInterface.class.php') !== '5de95b14c419a17b39e8c14ea69d53a2aa0e9fd4') {

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
	writefile_30();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php') != '13020c3bdd919b60b64aabc0b0719de5c3b3a224') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php') !== '13020c3bdd919b60b64aabc0b0719de5c3b3a224') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php') !== 'cc41dc225c5bd9e96906ba2a4abf7529b75bfdc1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php') !== '13020c3bdd919b60b64aabc0b0719de5c3b3a224') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMailUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_31();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != '017f51fe7a27bb6638ce2c3a4af47f89fca0d25a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '017f51fe7a27bb6638ce2c3a4af47f89fca0d25a') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '22af2512bcda91a168884c527afa51eb2e2743fe') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '017f51fe7a27bb6638ce2c3a4af47f89fca0d25a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php') !== '6cf83e8cc1693260a9eadf54c2c0a4dd9b384baa') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_54();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '0da5a0fb4752fa3a42d076d43840cbdb804d4b13') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '0da5a0fb4752fa3a42d076d43840cbdb804d4b13') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '9b6f57e70c6cb657152efa5b9e54ad99dc1743d7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '0da5a0fb4752fa3a42d076d43840cbdb804d4b13') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_57();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != '59074aa26c1c48743c951dfd18bc7279b5a4375d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '59074aa26c1c48743c951dfd18bc7279b5a4375d') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'a9e6b0b56794244ced7d5036834cbba6a8357540') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_57();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '59074aa26c1c48743c951dfd18bc7279b5a4375d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.css.php');
	writefile_58();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') != 'a9e7d036443d685fd1bcbb5ecdc120ce90ba6c20') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'a9e7d036443d685fd1bcbb5ecdc120ce90ba6c20') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'd5dd161ae1d8a26f7b8c34690d27277345993826') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_58();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'a9e7d036443d685fd1bcbb5ecdc120ce90ba6c20') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') != '8afe0bf86e33e75744ee4f781aaf0ae4bc9928c8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php', 0644)) {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_100();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') !== '8afe0bf86e33e75744ee4f781aaf0ae4bc9928c8') {

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml') != 'f060d202db3efa3376637f50e5bfe172ab8e0ed5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml') !== 'f060d202db3efa3376637f50e5bfe172ab8e0ed5') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml') !== 'd6f9e04bfbaf19977421ae533799c6fb58d25984') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_118();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml') !== 'f060d202db3efa3376637f50e5bfe172ab8e0ed5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/captcha/none/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml') != 'd76c7dd70831f4cbdb2b11f655dfc8f612e02e65') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml') !== 'd76c7dd70831f4cbdb2b11f655dfc8f612e02e65') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml') !== '39346adbe0b79a87f40470663b85df2cd7fdaf28') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_140();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml') !== 'd76c7dd70831f4cbdb2b11f655dfc8f612e02e65') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pdo/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

}
if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
	writefile_154();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml') != 'ca34498ab919d240e02b2f0f1a3c165943d5da8d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml') !== 'ca34498ab919d240e02b2f0f1a3c165943d5da8d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml') !== 'fda568dce41c86ccec76ffb45b8ad3b890479411') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_154();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml') !== 'ca34498ab919d240e02b2f0f1a3c165943d5da8d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
	writefile_181();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml') != '3e69cfac38090829cd0008a14969669eea5d2ac8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml') !== '3e69cfac38090829cd0008a14969669eea5d2ac8') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml') !== '5852654e9d9d0a37151402ca40dbf73e7e7ecefa') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_181();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml') !== '3e69cfac38090829cd0008a14969669eea5d2ac8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/gs1/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml');
	writefile_187();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml') != '4e5499eb02aa9a453072e38f1642515e6b997dbe') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml');
	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml') !== '4e5499eb02aa9a453072e38f1642515e6b997dbe') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml') !== '969cc416766dc076eabe2d3a2ba7f12beb375ca3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/ipv4/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');

		writefile_187();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml') != 'a2a1c962924fb056f90b8f5a98212f8b034dc7f6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml') !== 'a2a1c962924fb056f90b8f5a98212f8b034dc7f6') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml') !== 'fb5e58764119304c3e5e7aafeb13102697a82ea7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_199();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml') !== 'a2a1c962924fb056f90b8f5a98212f8b034dc7f6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/manifest.xml');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
	writefile_206();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml') != 'f4a176df3a4a2d90acd32a59600051ed8d8b08cf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml') !== 'f4a176df3a4a2d90acd32a59600051ed8d8b08cf') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml') !== '3f6a1703e06474df6d198f66db8d3101f68b8f3d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_206();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml') !== 'f4a176df3a4a2d90acd32a59600051ed8d8b08cf') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/manifest.xml');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/xml/vendor/robrichards/xmlseclibs/src/XMLSecEnc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_222();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/xml/vendor/robrichards/xmlseclibs/src/XMLSecEnc.php') !== 'cc51538202ee9ef949f9e5bf66a97d25a9893ca0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/xml/vendor/robrichards/xmlseclibs/src/XMLSecEnc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	writefile_227();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') != 'aaf6aba4c34679a59a36b2a6e6c47516c70ea1b1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== 'aaf6aba4c34679a59a36b2a6e6c47516c70ea1b1') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== '5597ec4dd7c43b9aa863bdfcf5866f984765e7dd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_227();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== 'aaf6aba4c34679a59a36b2a6e6c47516c70ea1b1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_230();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') != '4426d7721a8e004e9687d0a15719149bda691fc4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', 0644)) {

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '4426d7721a8e004e9687d0a15719149bda691fc4') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== 'da9de97bbcd47199e5a7173662350ab45d232c9c') {

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '4426d7721a8e004e9687d0a15719149bda691fc4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
		}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml') != 'e50f2d1bd936465fbe850722a8269b7de2ec384e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml') !== 'e50f2d1bd936465fbe850722a8269b7de2ec384e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml') !== '0fab5e2e7d25518695a246dc0cfa2ee538cd1c60') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_264();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml') !== 'e50f2d1bd936465fbe850722a8269b7de2ec384e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/manifest.xml');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	writefile_271();
	if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') != '781162ec32bcc868b7ad9fa9e26fd38f32c91a13') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/includes/setup_base.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '781162ec32bcc868b7ad9fa9e26fd38f32c91a13') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '25b8315f789e43f5e9cc2414aaa38acc9f0e6b66') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/includes/setup_base.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/includes/setup_base.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_271();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '781162ec32bcc868b7ad9fa9e26fd38f32c91a13') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
		}
	}
}
